  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK379">
<l>naṉṟāṅkā ṉallavāk kāṇpava raṉṟāṅkā</l>
<l>lallaṟ paṭuva tevaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>How is it that those, who are pleased with good fortune, trouble themselves when evil comes, (since both are equally the decree of fate) ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
